Spy BBC3
Series 1 Episodes 1 - 10 

VideoCodec: Theora [Thusnelda-alpha2]
Resolution:352x208 @25fps
AudioCodec: Vorbis 128kb/s 44100Hz stereo

AirDate:October 2004


Eight members of the public get the chance to find out as they undergo training in the art of subterfuge.  Spy is a 10-part series that will blow the lid on the secret world of intelligence and espionage. The programme gives ordinary people the chance to inhabit a world they have only ever read about or seen on screen.  Undergoing rigorous training parallel to that of intelligence operatives all over the world, eight candidates have the chance to leave their old lives behind, relocate to a new city and assume a whole new identity...

